      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no significant mechanical issues. There is minor cosmetic wear \u2014 small scratches or light paint blemishes \u2014 consistent with normal use. The interior is intact and functional. Overall a solid, reliable vehicle.",
